<h1> Goal </h1>
The goal of this project is the implementation of an image classification system with four classes (Ck in [airplane, motorbike, face, car]) using bag-of-words. 

<h1> Steps </h1>
The system contains the following steps:
<h2> Feature extraction and description</h2>
<h2> Building a visual vocabulary </h2>
<h2> Quantization of features using visual dictionary (encoding) </h2>
<h2> Representing images by frequencies of visual words </h2>
<h2> Classification </h2>